M|audience-architecture|name: audience-architecture
M|audience-architecture|description: YVON-specific layered audience stack for Novizio (Meta + TikTok) and Hourbour (LinkedIn + YouTube). Defines cold/lookalike/retargeting layers, exclusion rules, seed sources, and retargeti
M|audience-architecture|version: 1.0.0
M|audience-architecture|Generic audience targeting fails because it ignores two things: vtr-specific exclusion rules and the correct layering sequence. Running cold and retargeting simultaneously to the same user creates mes
M|audience-architecture|**Meta:**
M|audience-architecture|- Interest targeting: fashion, luxury fashion, sustainable fashion, street style, editorial fashion
M|audience-architecture|- Demographics: 22–45, all genders unless product-specific
M|audience-architecture|- Exclude: past purchasers (all time), website visitors (last 180 days), bargain/discount interests (coupon apps, sale alerts, fast fashion)
M|audience-architecture|- Minimum audience size: 500K before launching cold cg
M|audience-architecture|**TikTok:**
M|audience-architecture|- Interest: fashion, style, lifestyle, luxury
M|audience-architecture|- Behaviour: video completion rate > 75% on fashion cnt
M|audience-architecture|- Exclude: past purchasers if pixel data available
M|audience-architecture|- Minimum: 200K
M|audience-architecture|**Creative brief to Lena/Atlas:** Aspirational, editorial. Esteem and aspiration triggers. Never urgency or discount framing.
M|audience-architecture|**Seed sources (in priority order):**
M|audience-architecture|1. Purchaser email list — highest-quality seed
M|audience-architecture|2. Add-to-cart users (last 90 days) — second best
M|audience-architecture|3. Top 25% engagement audience (Instagram profile engagers) — if purchase list < 100 users
M|audience-architecture|**Minimum seed size:** 100 users. Below this threshold, the lookalike signal is unreliable — do not run.
M|audience-architecture|**Lookalike tiers:**
M|audience-architecture|- 1% lookalike: most similar to seed — highest intent, smallest audience
M|audience-architecture|- 1–3% lookalike: broader pool — more volume, slightly lower intent
M|audience-architecture|- Run both tiers as separate ad sets to identify which converts better
M|audience-architecture|**Exclusions:** Exclude actual purchasers and current website visitors from lookalike audiences.
M|audience-architecture|**Creative brief:** soc proof angle, product quality story. Still brand-first, not discount-first.
M|audience-architecture|**Window tiers (highest intent first):**
M|audience-architecture|| Audience | Window | Creative angle |
M|audience-architecture||---------|--------|---------------|
M|audience-architecture|| Checkout abandoners | 7 days | Product-specific, minimal friction CTA |
M|audience-architecture|| Add-to-cart, no purchase | 14 days | Product benefit reminder |
M|audience-architecture|| Product page visitors | 14 days | Brand credibility + product |
M|audience-architecture|| Video viewers (75%+ completion) | 30 days | Next step in funnel |
M|audience-architecture|| Instagram/TikTok engagers | 30 days | Brand story continuation |
M|audience-architecture|**Rule:** Retargeting always shows different creative from cold. If they've seen the brand, do not show the awareness ad again.
M|audience-architecture|**LinkedIn:**
M|audience-architecture|- Job titles: freelancer, independent consultant, contractor, agency owner, self-employed, founder (< 10 employees)
M|audience-architecture|- Company size: 1–10, 11–50
M|audience-architecture|- Geographic: English-speaking markets first (US, UK, CA, AU)
M|audience-architecture|- Exclude: enterprise job titles (VP, Director at 500+ companies), students, job seekers
M|audience-architecture|- Minimum audience size: 10K before launching on LinkedIn
M|audience-architecture|**YouTube:**
M|audience-architecture|- Custom intent audience: users who searched cp terms (Toggl, Harvest, Clockify, FreshBooks time tracking)
M|audience-architecture|- In-market: small business software, freelance tools
M|audience-architecture|- Exclude: existing trial users if matched via email
M|audience-architecture|**Creative brief:** Safety and trust triggers. "Always know where your hours went." Professional, not enthusiastic.
M|audience-architecture|Hourbour's audience is too small for meaningful lookalike. Skip straight to retargeting after cold.
M|audience-architecture|**Retargeting tiers:**
M|audience-architecture|| Audience | Window | Creative angle |
M|audience-architecture||---------|--------|---------------|
M|audience-architecture|| Pricing page visitors | 7 days | Specific outcome + soc proof |
M|audience-architecture|| Trial sign-ups — not activated | 7 days | Activation reminder, specific first step |
M|audience-architecture|| Trial sign-ups — active but not converting | 14 days | Value proof, what they'll lose at trial end |
M|audience-architecture|| Trial expired, not converted | 30 days | Win-back offer or extended trial |
M|audience-architecture|| Active paying customers | Excluded from all prospecting |
M|audience-architecture|**Win-back window:** 60–90 days for lapsed trials. Different message entirely — acknowledge the gap.
M|audience-architecture|1. **Never cold-target and retarget the same user simultaneously.** Audiences must be mutually exclusive — always add exclusion layers.
M|audience-architecture|2. **Never run lookalike from fewer than 100 seed users.** The signal is too weak to be reliable.
M|audience-architecture|3. **Exclude active paying customers from all prospecting and retargeting** — they're not a prospect.
M|audience-architecture|4. **Minimum audience size before launching:**
M|audience-architecture|- Meta cold: 500K
M|audience-architecture|- TikTok cold: 200K
M|audience-architecture|- LinkedIn: 10K
M|audience-architecture|- YouTube custom intent: 1K
M|audience-architecture|Below these thresholds, the platform can't optimise — CPMs rise and delivery stalls.
M|audience-architecture|5. **Novizio:** Never target discount or bargain-oriented interest segments. Conflicts with the brand positioning.
M|audience-architecture|6. **Hourbour:** Never target enterprise (500+ employee companies). Product is designed for solo/small team operators.
M|audience-architecture|| Intent level | Window | Signal |
M|audience-architecture||-------------|--------|--------|
M|audience-architecture|| Very high (checkout abandon, trial signup) | 7 days | Strongest buying signal |
M|audience-architecture|| High (product/pricing page) | 14 days | Clear consideration |
M|audience-architecture|| Medium (homepage, feature pages, video) | 30 days | Early interest |
M|audience-architecture|| Win-back (lapsed, churned) | 60–90 days | Re-engagement message required |